title: National Register of Historic Places listings in Washington County, Utah
text:
This is a list of the National Register of Historic Places listings in Washington County, Utah.
This is intended to be a complete list of the properties and districts on the <a href="National%20Register%20of%20Historic%20Places">National Register of Historic Places</a> in <a href="Washington%20County%2C%20Utah">Washington County</a>, <a href="Utah">Utah</a>, <a href="United%20States">United States</a>. Latitude and longitude coordinates are provided for many National Register properties and districts; these locations may be seen together in a map.
There are 78 properties and districts listed on the National Register in the county. Of these, 25 are located within <a href="Zion%20National%20Park">Zion National Park</a> and are described in <a href="National%20Register%20of%20Historic%20Places%20listings%20in%20Zion%20National%20Park">National Register of Historic Places listings in Zion National Park</a>. This list covers the 52 others. One other site in the county was once listed, but has since been removed.
